        "SW clear"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：CHAIN到FETCH是Next，CHAIN到COMPLETE是Last，COMPLETE到IDLE是IRQ sent，ERROR到IDLE是SW clear。这样整个IngressController的状态机就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
